[Civil No. 804.] YAVAPAI COUNTY, Appellant, v. JAMES P. STORM, Treasurer and Ex Officio Tax-Collector of Yavapai County, Appellee. APPEAL from the District Court of the Fourth Judicial District in and for the County of Yavapai. R. E. Sloan, Judge. James H. Wright, Attorney for Appellee. October 31, 1902.

No appearance for Appellant.

Dismissed.
